profile_summary:
SANU MUHAMMED C is a highly skilled software engineer with a strong foundation in languages such as C, C++, and Python. With a proven track record of building reliable and efficient solutions, Sanu has established himself as a trusted professional in the tech community, as evidenced by his 44 followers and 81 public repositories showcasing his active development. His technical expertise is complemented by a keen passion for solving real-world problems with innovative technology solutions.

As a dedicated developer, Sanu brings a unique combination of technical skills and entrepreneurial spirit to the table. Currently building at Fulva-in, he is committed to pushing the boundaries of what is possible with technology. With a background in Computer Science from CUSAT, Sanu possesses a solid understanding of the principles that drive the industry. His work is characterized by a relentless pursuit of excellence, a willingness to adapt, and a keen awareness of emerging trends and technologies, making him an invaluable asset to any organization or project.
